    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/357-adding-ssl">Adding SSL</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      It is important to protect a user&#x27;s private information with HTTPS. Here you will learn how to get it working on your local machine, configure Rack SSL, install certificates for production, and more.
