    </div>
    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/356-dangers-of-session-hijacking">Dangers of Session Hijacking</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      If a user&#x27;s authentication cookie is sent over an insecure connection it is vulnerable to session hijacking, or more specifically, sidejacking. Learn how this is done, and how you can prevent it.
      <span class="stats">(6 minutes)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="watch">
        <a href="/episodes/356-dangers-of-session-hijacking?autoplay=true" class="pretty_button">Watch Episode</a>
